{"html":"<hr>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理\">\n        <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#anchor-VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理\"><span class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>\n        VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理\n        </h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/volta-cli/volta\">VOLTA官网</a>  </p>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-安装\">\n        <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#anchor-安装\"><span class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>\n        安装\n        </h4>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-Bash\">brew install   \n</code></pre><h4 id=\"anchor-配置环境变量\">\n        <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#anchor-配置环境变量\"><span class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>\n        配置环境变量\n        </h4>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-Bash\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ~/.zshrc  </span>\n...  \n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> VOLTA_HOME=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$HOME</span>/.volta\"</span>  \n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> PATH=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$VOLTA_HOME</span>/bin:<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$PATH</span>\"</span>  \n...  \n</code></pre><h4 id=\"anchor-常用命令\">\n        <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#anchor-常用命令\"><span class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>\n        常用命令\n        </h4>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-Bash\">volta install node <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 安装最新版的node  </span>\nvolta install node@version <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 安装指定版本的node  </span>\n  \nvolta uninstall node@version <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 卸载  </span>\n  \nvolta pin node@12.20.2 <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 指定项目使用node的版本  </span>\nvolta pin yarn@1.19.2  \n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 会在package.json里添加  </span>\n<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"volta\"</span>: {  \n  <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"node\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"12.20.2\"</span>,  \n  <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"yarn\"</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"1.19.2\"</span>  \n}  \n  \n</code></pre><p><em>关注node的试验特性（包管理器的管理器） -  Corepack</em>  </p>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-必备软件\">\n        <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#anchor-必备软件\"><span class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>\n        必备软件\n        </h3>\n<ol>\n<li>vs code 编辑器  </li>\n<li>chrome 浏览器  </li>\n<li>inna 视频播放器  </li>\n<li>maccy 剪切板工具   </li>\n<li>obsidian 笔记工具  </li>\n<li>The Unarchiver 解压缩工具</li>\n</ol>\n","heading":[{"text":"VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理","level":3,"id":"anchor-VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理","children":[{"text":"安装","level":4,"id":"anchor-安装"},{"text":"配置环境变量","level":4,"id":"anchor-配置环境变量"},{"text":"常用命令","level":4,"id":"anchor-常用命令"}]},{"text":"必备软件","level":3,"id":"anchor-必备软件"}],"tokens":[{"type":"hr","raw":"---  \n"},{"type":"space","raw":"  \n"},{"type":"heading","raw":"### VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理  \n","depth":3,"text":"VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理","tokens":[{"type":"text","raw":"VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理","text":"VOLTA- javascript 工具链管理工具 主要用于node版本管理"}]},{"type":"space","raw":"  \n"},{"type":"paragraph","raw":"[VOLTA官网](https://github.com/volta-cli/volta)  ","text":"[VOLTA官网](https://github.com/volta-cli/volta)  ","tokens":[{"type":"link","raw":"[VOLTA官网](https://github.com/volta-cli/volta)","href":"https://github.com/volta-cli/volta","title":null,"text":"VOLTA官网","tokens":[{"type":"text","raw":"VOLTA官网","text":"VOLTA官网"}]},{"type":"text","raw":"  ","text":"  "}]},{"type":"space","raw":"\n  \n"},{"type":"heading","raw":"#### 安装  \n","depth":4,"text":"安装","tokens":[{"type":"text","raw":"安装","text":"安装"}]},{"type":"space","raw":"  \n"},{"type":"code","raw":"``` Bash  \nbrew install   \n```  \n","lang":"Bash","text":"brew install   "},{"type":"heading","raw":"#### 配置环境变量  \n","depth":4,"text":"配置环境变量","tokens":[{"type":"text","raw":"配置环境变量","text":"配置环境变量"}]},{"type":"space","raw":"  \n"},{"type"